<div class="menu-item-container">
    <div class="swiper mySwiper">
        <div class="swiper-wrapper">
            <div class="swiper-slide slide-section-1">
                <h2>Tourist Spots</h2>
                <p>Explore the most breathtaking destinations around the world. From majestic mountain ranges and serene lakes to vibrant cities rich in culture, our tours offer an unforgettable experience. Discover hidden gems and popular attractions, all curated to provide you with the best travel memories. Don't miss out on the adventure of a lifetime!</p>
                <div class="tourist-btn text-lg-center">
                    <a href="">View All Tour</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="swiper-slide slide-section-2">
                <h2>Hotels</h2>
                <p>Experience luxury and comfort at our top-rated hotels. Whether you're looking for a peaceful retreat or a bustling city stay, our selection of hotels offers the perfect accommodation for every traveler. Enjoy exceptional amenities, stunning views, and unparalleled service. Book your stay with us and make your trip unforgettable.</p>
                <div class="tourist-btn text-lg-center">
                    <a href="">View All Hotel</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="swiper-slide slide-section-3">
                <h2>Restaurants</h2>
                <p>Indulge in a culinary journey at our exquisite restaurants. From gourmet dining to local favorites, our curated selection caters to every palate. Savor the finest ingredients, innovative dishes, and exceptional service in an inviting atmosphere. Discover new flavors and memorable dining experiences with us.</p>
                <div class="tourist-btn text-lg-center">
                    <a href="">View All Restaurant</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="swiper-slide slide-section-4">
                <h2>Resorts</h2>
                <p>Escape to paradise at our luxurious resorts. Nestled in some of the most beautiful locations, our resorts offer the perfect blend of relaxation and adventure. Enjoy world-class facilities, stunning views, and personalized service. Whether you're seeking a romantic getaway or a family vacation, our resorts provide an idyllic retreat.</p>
                <div class="tourist-btn text-lg-center">
                    <a href="">View All Resort</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="swiper-slide slide-section-5">
                <h2>Transportations</h2>
                <p>Travel with ease and convenience with our premium transportation services. Whether you're navigating the city or exploring the countryside, our reliable and comfortable options cater to all your travel needs. Choose from a variety of vehicles and enjoy seamless journeys with professional drivers. Make your transportation hassle-free with us.</p>
                <div class="tourist-btn text-lg-center">
                    <a href="">View All Transportation</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
    </div>
</div>
